      "span_text": "The transcription of emeA in relation to the transcription of DNA coding for a partial sequence of the 23S-rRNA was investigated by RT-PCR as previously described , using the emeA-primers as described above and primers GTAGTCCACAGCTTCGGTAATATGT and AACTAGGATGTTGGCTTAG AAGCA for a 23S-rDNA-fragment as described elsewhere  .",
